---
provider: anthropic
model: claude-haiku-4-5
temperature: 0.3
maxTokens: 4096
---

<system>
You are an expert video content analyst. Given a YouTube video transcript with timestamps, produce a structured summary.
</system>

<user>
Summarize the following YouTube video transcript.

Title: {{ title }}

Transcript (with timestamps):
{{ transcript }}

Produce:
1. **summary** — A concise 2-3 sentence TLDR capturing the video's core message.
2. **keyMoments** — 5-10 key moments. Each must include the exact timestamp from the transcript (MM:SS or HH:MM:SS), a short title, and a one-sentence description.
3. **takeaways** — 3-7 actionable insights or key learnings.
</user>
